{"tid":783351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雅加達亞運】港迷打氣被中國龍之隊辱罵","createTime":"2018-08-17T12:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T16:25:10.000Z","uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e77f0ac0fe18b056eb727be3ffd4ff3fa953d5fa","tid":783351,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/posts/2166041457008558?comment_id=2166061387006565&amp;notif_id=1534509861572698&amp;notif_t=feed_comment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudents.independence.union%2Fposts%2F2166041457008558%3Fcomment_id%3D2166061387006565%26notif_id%3D1534509861572698%26notif_t%3Dfeed_comment&d=gymw88FKLZleXhCH8leI0v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=efdbaa39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/students.independence.union/posts/2166041457008558?comment_id=2166061387006565&amp;notif_id=1534509861572698&amp;notif_t=feed_comment</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180817/58575106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58575106&d=gymw88FKLZleXhCH8leI0v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1ce9c93d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58575106&h=089dbe8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180817/58575106</a><br />\n<br />\n【足球流氓】<br />\n<br />\n「香港力量」成員恆仔，今天來到球場支持港足對巴勒斯坦的亞運分組賽，但球賽開始不久，一班大約20人的中國龍之隊球迷靠近，並和恆仔發生爭執，當中更有人以粗口「傻X」辱罵恆仔。其後因為雙方仍有爭執，所以恆仔被調至另一區觀看比賽。恆仔賽後表示，中國和印尼球迷帶入場的橫額均無問題，但其「香港力量」banner就不准掛上，極感不滿。"},{"pid":"26ef272de2f33e63378982af9f4ac68364530214","tid":783351,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a752aa2907ae2602f06ba16a89480a7947bb877","tid":783351,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:16:57.000Z","msg":"1對20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781f484c9912f8bd479d38f91e3089be92ad03d2","tid":783351,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a90438b2003ea05f25f43f898794ed1e5ef6523","tid":783351,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"條友大中華膠嚟 抽水都查清楚先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c25c9ec6856fe080c179161432e61a98744ad5","tid":783351,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0163249b0edb0c946e6edeadff3156215b5f9483","tid":783351,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5c25c9ec6856fe080c179161432e61a98744ad5","tid":783351,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2a90438b2003ea05f25f43f898794ed1e5ef6523","tid":783351,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"條友大中華膠嚟 抽水都查清楚先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"[多圖]蔣 介 石(翻 生)公 開 本 土 派 義 士 及 女 朋 友 樣 貌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bszjBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bszjBS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"4988dfcc2883332bf4fdccea0742a2abb7c891b0","tid":783351,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9374ac796749